rComments: Her accent sometimes makes it hard to understand her, but she is thorough in her lectures and exams reflect exact material covered in class. She isn't a tough marker either!

One of the best professors I have had at uOttawa. She encourages us to think conceptually, and provides the practice and feedback to do so. She lectures very well, is very easy to understand, and genuinely wants her students to do well. She also is very contemporary and uses modern examples in her lectures. Very awesome prof!
